  <sec sec-type="data-availability" id="s3">
    <title>Data availability</title>
    <p>SPREAD 4 is an open-source software under the MIT License and can be accessed at <ext-link xlink:href="https://spreadviz.org/" ext-link-type="uri">https://spreadviz.org/</ext-link>. Its source code is available at <ext-link xlink:href="https://github.com/phylogeography/spread" ext-link-type="uri">https://github.com/phylogeography/spread</ext-link> for further software development or compiling the latest custom build. While the user interface and features of SPREAD are very intuitive, a web page with the most frequently asked questions can be found at <ext-link xlink:href="https://beast.community/spread4" ext-link-type="uri">https://beast.community/spread4</ext-link>.</p>
  </sec>
